.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.28</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.2</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.41 / 1.19</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.87</span></td><td>0.67</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.34</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.24</span></td><td>0.78</td><td>1.26</td><td>1.35</td><td>1.12</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.04</span></td><td>0.72</td><td>1.22</td><td>0.9</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.21</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.83</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.76</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 240 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 240 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>88.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>LOOKBACK_START</code></td><td><code>120</code></td><td>close.shift(120) — start of momentum window</td></tr><tr><td><code>LOOKBACK_END</code></td><td><code>240</code></td><td>close.shift(240) — end of momentum window</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9918</li>